title: Great Siege of Kings: Fight for Bohemia - Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Mod Gameplay
description:
The Kingdom of Bohemia is under siege!  The Kingdom of France and Toulouse have started a great military campaign against Bohemia.  The Duchy of Bavaria and the Kingdom of England join the defense.  This is the great siege of Kings!  Enjoy the battle :D

Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD is a mod for Total War Attila.   


If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
